    <title>OpenCV-Python教程(2) --- 图片的加载和显示</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/08/18/2018-08-18-OpenCV-Python%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-2-%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/08/18/2018-08-18-OpenCV-Python教程-2-图片的加载和显示/</id>
    <published>2018-08-18T07:05:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-08-18T13:26:16.357Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="OpenCV-Python教程-2-—-图片的加载和显示"><a href="#OpenCV-Python教程-2-—-图片的加载和显示" class="headerlink" title="OpenCV-Python教程(2) — 图片的加载和显示"></a>OpenCV-Python教程(2) — 图片的加载和显示</h2><h3 id="Targets"><a href="#Targets" class="headerlink" title="Targets"></a>Targets</h3><ul><li>加载图片，显示图片，保存图片</li><li>OpenCV函数：cv2.imread(), cv2.imshow(), cv2.imwrite()</li></ul><a id="more"></a><h3 id="Images-in-OpenCV"><a href="#Images-in-OpenCV" class="headerlink" title="Images in OpenCV"></a>Images in OpenCV</h3><p>OpenCV中彩色图是以B-G-R通道存储的，灰度图只有一个通道，图像坐标的起始点是在左上角：<br><img src="/2018/08/18/2018-08-18-OpenCV-Python教程-2-图片的加载和显示/cv2_image_coordinate_channels.jpg" alt=""></p><h3 id="Read-an-image"><a href="#Read-an-image" class="headerlink" title="Read an image"></a>Read an image</h3><p>使用<code>cv2.imread()</code>来读入一张图片：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cv2.imread(filename[, flags]) -&gt; retval</span><br><span class="line">@param: filename:</span><br><span class="line">    - 如果图片放在当前文件夹下，直接写文件名就行了，如&apos;lena.jpg&apos;</span><br><span class="line">    - 否则，需要给出绝对路径，如&apos;~/User/jinzhangyu/Desktop/lena.jpg&apos;</span><br><span class="line">@param: flags:</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.IMREAD_COLOR : 彩色图，只有RGB三个通道，默认值(1)</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.IMREAD_GRAYSCALE : 灰度图(0)</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.IMREAD_UNCHANGED : 还包含透明通道的彩色图，一般没啥用(-1)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对于图像处理来说，灰度图的应用远远比彩色图要多的多。<br><blockquote><p>经验之谈：路径中不能有中文，也最好不要有空格哦，并且没有加载成功的话是不会报错的，而是None，后面处理才会报错，算是个小坑</p></blockquote></p><h4 id="Example"><a href="#Example" class="headerlink" title="Example"></a>Example</h4><p>本图没有透明通道，即没有alpha通道</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Python <span class="number">3.5</span><span class="number">.4</span> |Continuum Analytics, Inc.| (default, Aug <span class="number">14</span> <span class="number">2017</span>, <span class="number">12</span>:<span class="number">43</span>:<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">[GCC <span class="number">4.2</span><span class="number">.1</span> Compatible Apple LLVM <span class="number">6.0</span> (clang<span class="number">-600.0</span><span class="number">.57</span>)] on darwin</span><br><span class="line">Type <span class="string">"help"</span>, <span class="string">"copyright"</span>, <span class="string">"credits"</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> <span class="string">"license"</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> more information.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> cv2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>img_1 = cv2.imread(<span class="string">'lena.jpg'</span>,<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>img_2 = cv2.imread(<span class="string">'lena.jpg'</span>,<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>img_3 = cv2.imread(<span class="string">'lena.jpg'</span>,<span class="number">-1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>img_1.shape</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">350</span>, <span class="number">350</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>img_2.shape</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">350</span>, <span class="number">350</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>img_3.shape</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">350</span>, <span class="number">350</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下面就是img_1,img_2,img_3的效果<br><img src="/2018/08/18/2018-08-18-OpenCV-Python教程-2-图片的加载和显示/imread.jpg" alt=""></p><h3 id="Display-an-image"><a href="#Display-an-image" class="headerlink" title="Display an image"></a>Display an image</h3><p>使用<code>cv2.imshow()</code>来显示一张图片，窗口会自适应图片的大小，紧接上面代码内容</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cv2.imshow(winname, mat) -&gt; None</span><br><span class="line">@param: winname:</span><br><span class="line">    Name of the window.</span><br><span class="line">@param: mat:</span><br><span class="line">    Image to be shown.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>单独使用上述函数还是不够的，我们需要人为控制窗口的展示时间，以及何时才能退出。所以<code>cv2.waitKey()</code>函数会被用到</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cv2.waitKey([delay]) -&gt; retval</span><br><span class="line">@param: delay:</span><br><span class="line">    - 是让程序暂停的意思，参数是等待时间（毫秒ms）。时间一到，会继续执行接下来的程序。</span><br><span class="line">    - 传入0的话表示一直等待.</span><br><span class="line">    - Since the macOS has a minimum time between switching threads,</span><br><span class="line">    the function will not wait exactly delay ms, it will wait at least delay ms</span><br><span class="line">    ,depending on what else is running on your computer at that time.</span><br><span class="line">@param: retval:</span><br><span class="line">    其返回值用以获取用户的按键输入，详情见后文Example部分</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意：必须鼠标点在cv2的展示窗口上，再键盘输入才会有效；如果鼠标点在Terminal上，再键盘输入进Terminal中是不会影响<code>cv2.waitKey()</code>的返回值的！</strong></p><p>在展示完图片后需要关闭所有的窗口，此时就需要<code>cv2.closeAllWindows()</code>函数。</p><p>当然如果什么都不做，直接结束Python程序的话，同样会关闭所有的窗口。这之中的区别只是，如果要打开一张图，关闭这张图，再打开新的一张图的话，就需要用到<code>cv2.closeAllWindows()</code>函数了。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cv2.closeAllWindows() -&gt; None</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Example-1"><a href="#Example-1" class="headerlink" title="Example"></a>Example</h4><p>加载一个灰度图，显示图片，按下‘s’键保存后退出，或者按下’q’键退出不保存</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> cv2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 读取灰度图</span></span><br><span class="line">  img = cv2.imread(<span class="string">'lena.jpg'</span>,<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 以lena为窗口名，展示这张图片</span></span><br><span class="line">  cv2.imshow(<span class="string">'lena'</span>,img)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 窗口一直不关闭，并且监视键盘输入的值</span></span><br><span class="line">  key = cv2.waitKey(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果输出q，代表 quit；如果输入s，代表 save then quit.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> key == ord(<span class="string">'q'</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.closeAllWindows()</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">elif</span> key == ord(<span class="string">'s'</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.imwrite(<span class="string">'1.jpg'</span>,img)</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.closeAllWindows()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Write-an-image"><a href="#Write-an-image" class="headerlink" title="Write an image"></a>Write an image</h3><p>写图像就相对简单了不少，只需使用<code>cv2.imwrite()</code>函数即可。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cv2.imwrite(filename, img[, params]) → retval</span><br><span class="line">@param: filename</span><br><span class="line">    Name of the file. 需要以图片格式结尾，例如‘lena.jpg’这样的字符串。</span><br><span class="line">@param: image</span><br><span class="line">    Image to be saved.</span><br><span class="line">@param: params</span><br><span class="line">    - For JPEG, it can be a quality ( cv2.IMWRITE_JPEG_QUALITY ) from 0 to 100</span><br><span class="line">     (the higher is the better). Default value is 95.</span><br><span class="line">    - For PNG, it can be the compression level ( CV_IMWRITE_PNG_COMPRESSION )</span><br><span class="line">     from 0 to 9. A higher value means a smaller size and longer compression</span><br><span class="line">     time. Default value is 3.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Nice，是不是很简单呐，再接再厉噢(●’◡’●)</p><h3 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h3><p><a href="http://ex2tron.top/2017/12/06/Python-OpenCV教程2：基本元素-图片/#引用" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EX2TRON’S BLOG: Python-OpenCV 教程2：基本元素-图片</a><br><a href="https://www.kancloud.cn/aollo/aolloopencv/259610" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenCV-Python 中文教程: OpenCV的图像读取显示及保存</a><br><a href="https://opencv-python-tutroals.readthedocs.io/en/latest/py_tutorials/py_gui/py_image_display/py_image_display.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> OpenCV-Python 官方教程: Getting Started with Images</a></p>]]></content>
    
